  <RNGun_AR23ChaosLiberator_Rifle.label>AR-23“混沌解放者”</RNGun_AR23ChaosLiberator_Rifle.label>
  <!-- EN: The AR-23 Liberator (Repainted and renamed by Chaos Divers to "Chaos Liberator") is a 5.56x45mm SEAF, gas-operated, magazine-fed assault rifle with a 16.5 in barrel and adjustable stock. Known for its durability and stopping power, it’s a Helldivers favorite for its adaptability in harsh combat conditions. The Mk2 variant features reinforced internals and a quick-swap barrel system. -->
  <RNGun_AR23ChaosLiberator_Rifle.description>AR-23“混沌解放者”（由ChaosDivers重新涂装并更名为混沌解放者”）以其耐用性和强大的制动力而闻名，并因其在严酷战斗条件下的适应性而深受绝地潜兵的青睐。</RNGun_AR23ChaosLiberator_Rifle.description>
