  <RNGun_AR23LiberatorPenetrator_Rifle.label>AR-23P穿甲“解放者”</RNGun_AR23LiberatorPenetrator_Rifle.label>
  <!-- EN: The AR-23 Liberator Penetrator is a 5.56×45mm SEAF assault rifle modified for increased armor penetration. Featuring a reinforced barrel, tuned gas system, and hardened bolt assembly, the Penetrator trades some fire rate for superior punch-through against medium armor. Field-proven and reliable, it’s a trusted upgrade for Helldivers expecting heavier resistance. -->
  <RNGun_AR23LiberatorPenetrator_Rifle.description>改装后的AR-23P穿甲“解放者”搭配瞄准镜，可发射穿甲弹，助力使用者击倒装备护甲的目标。</RNGun_AR23LiberatorPenetrator_Rifle.description>
