  <!-- EN: LAS-16 Sickle -->
  <RNGun_LAS16Sickle_Rifle.label>LAS-16“镰刀”</RNGun_LAS16Sickle_Rifle.label>
  <!-- EN: The LAS-16 Sickle is a high-energy laser rifle designed for precision and sustained fire. It features a compact frame, advanced cooling systems, and adjustable optics for versatility in various combat scenarios. Reliable and efficient, the LAS-16 is a preferred choice for Helldivers facing energy-resistant threats. -->
  <RNGun_LAS16Sickle_Rifle.description>LAS-16镰刀是一款专为精准射击和持续射击而设计的可瞬间喷射高能激光束的激光步枪。它拥有紧凑的枪身、先进的冷却系统和可调节的光学元件，可在各种战斗场景中灵活运用。LAS-16“镰刀”可靠高效，是绝地潜兵面对轻甲威胁的首选。</RNGun_LAS16Sickle_Rifle.description>
